{"tid":1991634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭偉健被換走 司法機構：留意到社會上爭議 所以作出有關安排","createTime":"2020-04-27T14:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T01:27:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":176,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"789c303e1987b58ec4973a433e3532526cca9114","tid":1991634,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"剛於上周五（ 4 月 24 日）審理將軍澳「連儂隧道」斬人案的區域法院法官郭偉健，原定今午處理另一宗涉及反修例運動的案件，聽取對控罪的回答，但突被換走，改由首席區域法院法官高勁修處理。司法機構回覆《立場新聞》時表示，「首席區域法院法官留意到最近社會上對郭偉健法官審理的某宗案件的判刑理由有爭議，所以現階段作出有關安排。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9B%BE%E8%AE%9A%E6%96%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8E%E9%81%8A-%E6%83%85%E6%93%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%9A-%E9%83%AD%E5%81%89%E5%81%A5%E6%96%BC%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%9B%E8%B5%B0-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B-%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E5%88%B0%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8A%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%2596%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2581%258A-%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2593%258D%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B0%259A-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%259B%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B-%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4YCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=b7871a30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%2596%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2581%258A-%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2593%258D%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B0%259A-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%